## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-102">Windows 桌面語音的集合形式傳回已辨識的片語<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-102">Windows Desktop Speech returns recognized phrases as collections of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-103">每個物件會對應至單一字詞或標點符號。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-103">Each object corresponds to a single word or punctuation mark.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-104">`DisplayAttributes`的屬性<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit>或是<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText>使用的成員<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DisplayAttributes>列舉型別來描述如何列印間距處理給定的斷或標點符號周圍。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-104">The `DisplayAttributes` property of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.ReplacementText> uses a member of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DisplayAttributes> enumeration to describe how print spacing is handled around a given word or punctuation mark.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-105">兩個或多個成員`DisplayAttributes`列舉型別可能會結合的位元`OR`來指定應該顯示特定字詞的方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-105">Two or more members of the `DisplayAttributes` enumeration may be combined by a bit-wise `OR` to specify how a particular word should be displayed.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-106">顯示格式，語音辨識器所使用的是特定的語言。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-106">The display formatting that the speech recognizer uses is language specific.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-107">例如，假設要使用預設系統文法所提供的辨識引擎的輸入的片語<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar>是 「 Hello 逗號期間他說: 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-107">For example, suppose the input phrase to a recognition engine using the default system grammar provided by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> is "Hello comma he said period".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-108">則會傳回辨識引擎<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>包含五<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit>物件包含下列字串取代為下列`DisplayAttributes`值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-108">Then the recognition engine returns a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> containing five <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> objects containing the following strings with the following `DisplayAttributes` values.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-109">項目</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-109">Item</span></span>|`DisplayAttributes`|  
|----------|-------------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-110">Hello</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-110">Hello</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-111">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-111">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-112">,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-112">,</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-113">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-113">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-114">he</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-114">he</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-115">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-115">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-116">說</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-116">said</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-117">OneTrailingSpace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-117">OneTrailingSpace</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-118">。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-118">.</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="c36cf-119">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-119">OneTrailingSpace &#124; ConsumeLeadingSpaces</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-120">針對此辨識的片語會印為傳回的文字:"Hello，他說。"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-120">The text returned for this recognized phrase is printed as: "Hello, he said."</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c36cf-121">下列範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit.DisplayAttributes%2A>屬性的一份<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit>句子格式化文字的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c36cf-121">The following example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit.DisplayAttributes%2A> property of a list of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedWordUnit> objects to format the words as a phrase.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
// Use the DisplayAttributes property to format speech as text.   
  
static string GetDisplayText(List<RecognizedWordUnit> words)  
{  
  StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();  
  
  // Concatenate the word units together. Use the DisplayAttributes  
  // property of each word unit to add or remove white space around  
  // the word unit.  
  foreach (RecognizedWordUnit word in words)  
  {  
    if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.ConsumeLeadingSpaces) != 0))  
    {  
      sb = new StringBuilder(sb.ToString().TrimEnd());  
    }  
  
    sb.Append(word.Text);  
  
    if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.OneTrailingSpace) != 0)  
    {  
      sb.Append(" ");  
    }  
    else if ((word.DisplayAttributes  
      & DisplayAttributes.TwoTrailingSpaces) != 0)  
    {  
      sb.Append("  ");  
    }  
  }  
  
  return sb.ToString();  
}  
  
```
